# Revision history for Perl extension MP3::InfoTag.

0.40    2012-04-09

- tag2string(), string2tag(): normalize all placeholders in input patterns
  to upper case so that the placeholders are now case-insensitive
- minor refactoring in tag2string() concering max field length warning

0.31    2009-12-30

- changed packaging only, no changes of the module itself

0.30    2006-09-29

- new optional parameter `weed' for string2tag(): all matches of this regular
  expression will be replaced by spaces
- removed implicit replacement of underscores with spaces in string2tag();
  use the new weed parameter to do this explicitly

0.20    2005-05-13

- refactoring from OO module to `classic' module because this turned out to be
  a mere collections of functions

0.11    2004-11-14

- bug fix in string2tag(): seperator at end of pattern now possible

0.10    2004-10-17

- several undocumented early bug fixes since 0.01
- TAG_FIELDS_ORDERED holding sensible field order
- new: getTagFieldNames()
- changed order of fields in printTag() result string

0.01    2004-01-22

- initial version
